To start a Grid Scheduler:
    gradle gs -Pargv="['<gsName>']"

    e.g.:
    $ gradle gs -Pargv="['gs1']"

To start a Cluster:
    gradle rm -Pargv="['<rmName>', '<numNodes>', '<registryHost>', '<registryPort>', '<gsName>']"

    e.g.:
    $ gradle rm -Pargv="['rm1', '10', '127.0.0.1', '1099', 'gs1']"
